      <![CDATA[<h2 id="Enumeration"><a href="#Enumeration" class="headerlink" title="Enumeration"></a>Enumeration</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">nmap -A<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Privilege-Escalation-Exploit-runc"><a href="#Privilege-Escalation-Exploit-runc" class="headerlink" title="Privilege Escalation: Exploit runc"></a>Privilege Escalation: Exploit runc</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">babywyrm@giveback:/dev/shm/exploit$ <span class="hljs-built_in">ls</span><br>alpine.tar<br><br>babywyrm@giveback:/dev/shm/exploit$ <span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> rootfs<br>babywyrm@giveback:/dev/shm/exploit$ tar -xvf alpine.tar -C rootfs (slient)<br>babywyrm@giveback:/dev/shm/exploit$ <span class="hljs-built_in">ls</span> -la rootfs/<br>total 0<br>drwxrwxr-x 19 babywyrm babywyrm  400 Feb 24 12:50 .<br>drwxrwxr-x  3 babywyrm babywyrm  100 Feb 24 15:04 ..<br>-rwxr-xr-x  1 babywyrm babywyrm    0 Feb 24 12:45 .dockerenv<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm 1680 Jan 27 21:19 bin<br>drwxr-xr-x  4 babywyrm babywyrm  100 Feb 24 12:45 dev<br>drwxr-xr-x 17 babywyrm babywyrm  760 Feb 24 12:45 etc<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 home<br>drwxr-xr-x  6 babywyrm babywyrm  160 Jan 27 21:19 lib<br>drwxr-xr-x  5 babywyrm babywyrm  100 Jan 27 21:19 media<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 mnt<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 opt<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 proc<br>drwx------  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 root<br>drwxr-xr-x  3 babywyrm babywyrm   60 Jan 27 21:19 run<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm 1280 Jan 27 21:19 sbin<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 srv<br>drwxr-xr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 sys<br>drwxrwxr-x  2 babywyrm babywyrm   40 Jan 27 21:19 tmp<br>drwxr-xr-x  7 babywyrm babywyrm  140 Jan 27 21:19 usr<br>drwxr-xr-x 11 babywyrm babywyrm  260 Jan 27 21:19 var<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2026/02/25/HackTheBox-GiveBack-Linux-Medium/htb-giveback.png" class="" title="Nmap Scan width&#x3D;700">]]>
